{"tid":753353,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"返工會令自己忘記一大部分","createTime":"2018-07-23T13:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T14:18:09.000Z","uid":195167,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e80cb8c3a61f3bdc27bc3c9576e4df68c57b7ccd","tid":753353,"uid":195167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:47:59.000Z","msg":"原本以為自己要好耐先走得出傷痛<br />\n好彩份工一至六都忙過狗 無時間俾自己諗起你<br />\n比起頭幾日訓醒又喊 喊完又訓<br />\n但隨住有工返 有野做 時間好似返返去從沒遇見你之前。呢段日子發現身邊既朋友、至親既愛幾咁無微不至，到直家我開始接受到你一個過客呢個事實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 安慰自己其實你只係中意人對自己好，<br />\n講過既承諾做唔到都係bull shit,<br />\n由你傷害我個一刻開始你已經唔係最初我愛既你。<br />\n以前睇到你對個曖味過既人就算一齊唔到都大大段野講 到我地完結既一刻你得返一句:對唔住，到此為止。<br />\n第一個禮拜我都不停怪自己邊度做得唔好、放低尊嚴挽留一個唔愛既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多關係付出真心既善良人係會傷得最深。<br />\n<br />\n希望所有失戀既人都努力做野充實自己，<br />\n唔好俾自己亂諗野，&rdquo;好好過&rdquo;知易行難。<br />\n分開後好多愛情遺物都拋入咗垃圾桶，<br />\n只係有時經過回憶既地方仲會心戚戚下，<br />\n有時發夢會見返前度。<br />\n我都好努力咁生活 交俾時間去撫平傷口，雖然我知道個疤痕呢世都會跟住我。<br />\n<br />\n從今以後努力做人<br />\n耐心等到終點的那刻再擁抱 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=JHlp475dcf0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJHlp475dcf0&d=9QPT0drjuQgb%2FdNg2gLAoCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f459a66e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=JHlp475dcf0</a>"},{"pid":"a55fca8f7d81c1d4199e5bb36918b7d0a9cc824e","tid":753353,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"當呢度ig定facebook?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77d565cb7f7ccfc18f5b02589ab435dafe0dc20","tid":753353,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"日日ot到10點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f257746ecb21a38bb6f4853091423b80011826","tid":753353,"uid":195167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b77d565cb7f7ccfc18f5b02589ab435dafe0dc20","tid":753353,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"日日ot到10點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"8點返到屋企準時開到飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd002e4b450e6e89df0fdd68564d8a354da242d","tid":753353,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"夠鐘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a5a8609a1a0a04120600c0549f769f698abd83","tid":753353,"uid":195167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd002e4b450e6e89df0fdd68564d8a354da242d","tid":753353,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"夠鐘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"夠鐘死心了 當你沉默得高調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c364013ab77533fef20b53b39bc00adc40fcce","tid":753353,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5a5a8609a1a0a04120600c0549f769f698abd83","tid":753353,"uid":195167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd002e4b450e6e89df0fdd68564d8a354da242d","tid":753353,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"夠鐘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"夠鐘死心了 當你沉默得高調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"陣間有咩搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c79822e84adacdc5197240816d7cc217dcef37","tid":753353,"uid":195167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c364013ab775